      "created_at": "2023-12-21T03:55:07.424Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I really don\u2019t have any need for warmup/cooldown/active/rest (although I like the open-ended option for workouts I would take outside).  What would be most helpful is to have some kind of option to control the auto-switching behavior.  Maybe there was an additional \u201cauto\u201d button on the app (next to HR/ERG/SLOPE) that would auto-switch based on the mode specified in the workout and the specific mode buttons are \u201csticky\u201d and override the mode written in the workout.</p>",
